## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project presents a **Sales Performance Analysis Dashboard** built using **Power BI**.  
The goal of the project is to analyze sales data to understand **customer performance, product demand, sales trends, and profitability**.

The dashboard provides actionable insights that can help business stakeholders make data-driven decisions.

---

## ğŸ—‚ï¸ Dataset Description
- **Data Type:** Sales transaction data
- **Key Fields Include:**
  - Customer Name
  - Product Name
  - Units Sold
  - Sales Count
  - Profit
  - Date / Day of Week

The dataset was cleaned and transformed using **Power Query** before analysis.

