## ğŸ“ˆ Dashboard Insights
### ğŸ”¹ Customer Analysis
- Sales count and profit are broken down by customer
- Helps identify **high-value customers**

### ğŸ”¹ Product Performance
- Analysis of total units sold per product
- Identifies **best-selling and low-performing products**

### ğŸ”¹ Sales Trend Analysis
- Daily sales trends visualized using bar charts
- Weekly sales distribution highlights peak sales days

### ğŸ”¹ Profit Analysis
- Total profit across customers
- Supports revenue optimization decisions

